    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the 3.8L naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), delivering a linear power band and 385 hp. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp, short-throw engagement with a perfectly weighted clutch. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative: the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system maintains factory-spec damping, and the limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque vectoring. Zero evidence of bore scoring or oil migration; the undercarriage is pristine with all factory cosmoline intact. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
