    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish. Inside, the Agate Grey leather interior remains taut and retains its original factory scent, with no signs of wear on the bolsters or steering wheel. Mechanically, the car is perfect; it has been serviced exclusively at Porsche authorized centers, with all records available for inspection. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The 19-inch Boxster S wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands a vehicle with zero compromises and a complete, documented history.",
